{"tid":2026811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 繼續思想武裝自己，分化狗唔會停手","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:12:15.000Z","uid":48234,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"287955160c5be74230d8d907c7e67ebfa6129ed1","tid":2026811,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"老鳳有足夠耐力<br />\n分化狗對老鳳密集攻擊咗好耐<br />\n佢哋知道全無效果之後而家已經敗走<br />\n<br />\n但係咁樣即係其他手足可能會受到攻擊<br />\n請自己小心<br />\n無論係黃店老闆，定係地下組織，定係一般和理非都好，全部都有機會受到攻擊<br />\n請各位手足繼續全力支援其他手足<br />\n做得幾多得幾多<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈係現時最有效手段，所以一定係對家重點打擊對象<br />\n要全力保護，全力支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fa4a792146cf46a0753715bd381e4805a54709","tid":2026811,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力支持「35+」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張超雄、楊岳橋、黃碧雲、梁耀忠，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一票都不能少！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d42b4906f65cac20a344c58aee5b5c871a2d83d","tid":2026811,"uid":209225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78fa4a792146cf46a0753715bd381e4805a54709","tid":2026811,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力支持「35+」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張超雄、楊岳橋、黃碧雲、梁耀忠，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一票都不能少！</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"玩左35+<br />\n就玩唔到其他戰線？<br />\n抗爭得一條路？"},{"pid":"e2da2fa074344e3761cf5757e2c658f7c1152784","tid":2026811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d42b4906f65cac20a344c58aee5b5c871a2d83d","tid":2026811,"uid":209225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78fa4a792146cf46a0753715bd381e4805a54709","tid":2026811,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span sty